                                                                <customfield id="customfield_12310192" key="com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.customfieldtypes:textarea">
                        <customfieldname>Release Note</customfieldname>
                        <customfieldvalues>
                            <customfieldvalue>This module subsumes the current CSVLoader(). However, its syntax for escaping embedded double quotes is to prepend a second double quote. This syntax is the one honored by Excel 2007. In addition, this module&amp;#39;s default field delimiter is a comma. In part, this decision is based on Excel behaving inconsistently with newlines embedded in fields when tab is used as the delimiter. That delimiter default differs from the existing CSVLoader(), which defaults to tab for delimiting fields.</customfieldvalue>

                        </customfieldvalues>
